Banca Popolare di Milano Scrl
modified its new statute due to be voted on by shareholders on
Oct. 22 to accommodate requests by the  Bank of Italy , the bank
said yesterday in a statement.  The central bank asked Popolare di Milano to make changes
to guarantee a clear separation between ownership and
management, give shareholders a bigger role and strengthen the
